Subject: [PATCH 1240/2588] drivers/gpu/drm/i915/i915_gem.c: Add missing error
 handling code

Extend the error handling code with operations found in other nearby error
handling code

A simplified version of the sematic match that finds this problem is as
follows: (http://coccinelle.lip6.fr/)

// <smpl>
@r exists@
@r@
statement S1,S2,S3;
constant C1,C2,C3;
@@

*if (...)
 {... S1 return -C1;}
...
*if (...)
 {... when != S1
    return -C2;}
...
*if (...)
 {... S1 return -C3;}
// </smpl>

